data.description: Step into charm and comfort with this single-story home. Boasting 2 bed, 1 bath, and sunroom full of amazing natural light, this is the epitome of cozy living. Spacious lot, the property offers room to breathe and embrace outdoor living. Bring your puppies to run & garden to plant. Picture yourself enjoying coffee in the sunroom or hosting gatherings in the expansive backyard, think fire pit nights. Convenient freeway access to JBLM and I-5, a commuting breeze, you will have more time to savor the comforts of home. Every corner exudes good vibes. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming abode yours. Perfect blend of convenience and warmth. All appliances stay. Lots great updates. Investors & Veterans be sure to check this one out!
